00:40:36,599 --> 00:40:37,300
why don't we

591
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:38,780
stick together

592
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:40,260
and keep each other warm?

593
00:40:43,539 --> 00:40:44,219
What do you mean?

594
00:40:46,159 --> 00:40:47,000
I'll be blunt.

595
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:50,059
Your pool hall,

596
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:51,440
great location,

597
00:40:51,579 --> 00:40:52,300
makes good money.

598
00:40:52,780 --> 00:40:54,579
Naturally, a lot of people are jealous.

599
00:40:54,940 --> 00:40:55,360
Right?

600
00:40:55,559 --> 00:40:56,800
Look, my boys here,

601
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:57,880
they can keep an eye on the place for you.

602
00:40:58,360 --> 00:40:58,840
Alright?

603
00:40:59,260 --> 00:41:00,179
Keep warm.

604
00:41:01,019 --> 00:41:02,099
It won't cost much.

605
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:04,179
Thirty percent of the profits.

606
00:41:05,059 --> 00:41:06,599
Think of it as tea and snack money.

607
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:07,699
Tea and snack money?

608
00:41:08,179 --> 00:41:09,380
Why not call it alimony?

609
00:41:09,380 --> 00:41:11,320
We're all laid off and unemployed, right?

610
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:15,119
Sorry, Gordo.

611
00:41:16,300 --> 00:41:17,019
The pool hall

612
00:41:17,340 --> 00:41:18,659
I opened for a few brothers.

613
00:41:19,099 --> 00:41:20,019
The profit shares are fixed.

614
00:41:20,639 --> 00:41:21,480
As for tea and snack money,

615
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:22,840
whatever you drink or eat

616
00:41:22,840 --> 00:41:23,739
in my shop,

617
00:41:24,019 --> 00:41:24,719
it's on me.

618
00:41:25,380 --> 00:41:25,960
Put it on my tab.

619
00:41:29,219 --> 00:41:29,900
Good.

620
00:41:30,260 --> 00:41:30,960
Good.

621
00:41:32,380 --> 00:41:33,260
Come, come.

622
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:37,019
If you treat me as a brother,

623
00:41:37,019 --> 00:41:37,940
that's enough.

624
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:40,500
Having more friends

625
00:41:41,719 --> 00:41:43,579
is always better than having more enemies.

626
00:41:46,440 --> 00:41:47,000
Yi.
